description: Nestled in the gorgeous city of Kissimmee, FL, Storey Creek is a master-planned community with collections of new single-family homes for sale.

amenities.name: Swimming Pool
amenities.description: Cool off on hot summer days or get a workout in at the community swimming pool

amenities.name: Clubhouse
amenities.description: The clubhouse is a great place to gather with neighbors and friends

amenities.name: Fitness Center
amenities.description: The onsite fitness center features a variety of equipment, allowing residents to get any kind of workout in

amenities.name: Dog Park
amenities.description: Furry friends will love going to the dog park

amenities.name: Tot Lot
amenities.description: The playground is ideal for allowing kids to play and interact with friends

amenities.name: Basketball Court
amenities.description: Shoot some hoops or enjoy a friendly pick-up game at the basketball court

amenities.name: Tennis Court
amenities.description: Work on your serve or play a match with friends at the onsite tennis courts

amenities.name: Volleyball Court
amenities.description: Enjoy the sand and sun while playing a friendly game at the community volleyball court
